This plugin is an independent, unofficial educational tool. It implements and
teaches the "Running Lean" methodology created by Ash Maurya (Running Lean,
O'Reilly Media), which builds on Eric Ries's The Lean Startup, Steve Blank's
Customer Development, and Alex Osterwalder's Business Model Canvas. All credit
for the methodology belongs to its authors. Please read the book and support
the source: https://www.leanfoundry.com/books/running-lean

